posts.title: I'll take the downvotes, but I'm more afraid of what happens if I don't say something. I've "received" three signs so far that "something" bad may be coming and I've no idea what to think.
posts.content:
Let me preface and say I'm not a religious person, I'm honestly lost in what's going on.

I can prove this as I have some text messages with my sister who is a devout Catholic and I had to ask her what this could possibly mean, I was rather disturbed Monday morning.

Last Sunday night I had the most bizarrely vivid dream telling me it was urgent that I read Ezekiel 33. I don't know hardly any books of the Bible other than what I read as a child, I would never be able to quote anything specific like a chapter of a particular book. So a message so specific where I would've never come up with the name or chapter on my own like this, is personally bizarre in my world. I've never read Ezekiel and barely know the name. This came out of left field and I can't explain it.

My sister's reaction was she ordered me a "daily prayer devotional" so I could start praying to God for answers.

Then Tuesday night I had another extremely vivid dream where these "beings" took me on a ride in a car (the driver had four feet lol), and straight up told me "pay attention, something bad is coming". They showed me some pamphlets that had images of stranger's faces that I've never seen before, (also said something about a "bear"?)

Cue to this morning when I just received the devotional my sister ordered for me and I opened it to today's date, I just got smacked in the face once again... it's about Ezekiel 33.

It says " It was critical that the people be alerted as soon as possible to what is coming". "If you are spiritually alert, you may receive a warning from God that addresses specific dangers that those around you are facing". "If you are oblivious to God's message, those around you may miss the encouraging promise from God that He wanted to share through you. God holds His watchmen accountable for their diligence. Strive to be attentive to every word that comes to you from God..."

Now I'm not claiming anything other than stating this is happening. I'm super confused and lost by all this. They're just vague dreams and a coincidence right? It doesn't even clarify what "bad thing is coming"

I don't know what it means or what to do, but I think it would be reprehensible if this is real, and I didn't share this with those that will listen. Hopefully I'm wrong and just going slightly cuckoo lol.

You don't have to take me seriously or believe me, I know I wouldn't if this wasn't directly happening in my life.

I'm open to any interpretations or feedback (even "take your meds" lol), this kind of thing is not in my typical wheelhouse. I believe in God, but I'm not religious enough to understand this situation.
